      <title>穆迪将美国银行体系的展望从负面调整为稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/moodys-changes-outlook-us-banking-system-stable-negative-2024-10-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[评级机构穆迪周一将美国银行体系的评级展望从负面上调至稳定，称这一变化反映了人们对降息和持续温和的经济增长将稳定银行资产质量并推动盈利能力的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/moodys-changes-outlook-us-banking-system-stable-negative-2024-10-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 23:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
